== Installing as a simple-build-tool plugin

Add the following lines to your plugins definition:
  
  val sbtDeployRepo = "sbt-deploy-repo" at "http://reaktor.github.com/sbt-deploy/maven"
  val sbtDeploy = "fi.reaktor" % "sbt-deploy" % "0.1.0-SNAPSHOT"

or if it does not exist, create it, under project/build/plugins/Plugins.scala:

  import sbt._

  class Plugins(info: ProjectInfo) extends PluginDefinition(info) {
    val sbtDeployRepo = "sbt-deploy-repo" at "http://reaktor.github.com/sbt-deploy/maven"
    val sbtDeploy = "fi.reaktor" % "sbt-deploy" % "0.1.0-SNAPSHOT"
  }
